name: 064 Look at that code
description:
"I'm obsessed with feedbacks, in every way we can see it. Here is a classic idea (for me): show the code of my project into my visual. I do it a lot in my VJ performances, I love sharing for a little moment what I really see all day long working on my VJ sets, between some stroboscopic effects. (And if I live code this is way way cooler ahah). It's like showing the audience the guts of things

The real.

The reality of something.

Enjoy the abyss of it.

Enjoy the fbk"
